
This module adds each user after registration to the groups defined 
in the settings.


Installation instructions:
--------------------------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "register_to_group" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Configure the module through the module's settings page.

- Enable the module "Register To Group".


